OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779048354
OL,3,CDivers search for bodies of Italian
OL,4,Cdivers who died during cave dive in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FDivers in the Maldives have resumed
OL,8,Fthe search for the bodies of four
OL,9,FItalian divers believed to be deep
OL,10,Finside an underwater cave, after rough
OL,11,Fweather repeatedly hampered the effort
OL,12,Fthe previous day.
OL,14,FMaldives Presidential Spokesman
OL,15,FMohammed Hussain Shareef said that the
OL,16,Fsearchers have prepared a plan based
OL,17,Fon their progress exploring the cave
OL,18,Fon Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779048354
OL,3,CDivers search for bodies of Italian
OL,4,Cdivers who died during cave dive in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FItaly's Foreign Ministry said earlier
OL,8,Fthat the dive group are believed to
OL,9,Fhave died while exploring a cave at a
OL,10,Fdepth of about 50 metres in Vaavu
OL,11,FAtoll on Thursday.
OL,13,FItalian Foreign Minister Antonio
OL,14,FTajani said everything possible would
OL,15,Fbe done to bring the victims home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779048354
OL,3,CDivers search for bodies of Italian
OL,4,Cdivers who died during cave dive in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FHis ministry said it was coordinating
OL,8,Fwith Divers Alert Network, a
OL,9,Fspecialist diving organisation, to
OL,10,Fsupport recovery operations and the
OL,11,Frepatriation of the bodies. The cause
OL,12,Fof the deaths remains under
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779048354
OL,3,CDivers search for bodies of Italian
OL,4,Cdivers who died during cave dive in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FThe victims have been identified as
OL,8,FMonica Montefalcone, an associate
OL,9,Fecology professor at the University of
OL,10,FGenoa; her daughter Giorgia Sommacal;
OL,11,Fmarine biologist Federico Gualtieri;
OL,12,Fresearcher Muriel Oddenino; and diving
OL,13,Finstructor Gianluca Benedetti,
OL,14,Faccording to the Maldivian government.
OL,16,FBenedetti's body was recovered on
OL,17,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779048354
OL,3,CDivers search for bodies of Italian
OL,4,Cdivers who died during cave dive in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FMontefalcone and Oddenino were in the
OL,8,FMaldives on an official scientific
OL,9,Fmission to monitor marine environments
OL,10,Fand study the effects of climate
OL,11,Fchange on tropical biodiversity, the
OL,12,FUniversity of Genoa said in a
OL,13,Fstatement Friday.
OL,15,FIt added, however, that the scuba
OL,16,Fdiving activity during which the
OL,17,Fdeadly accident occurred was not part
OL,18,Fof the planned research and was
OL,19,F"undertaken privately."
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779048354
OL,3,CDivers search for bodies of Italian
OL,4,Cdivers who died during cave dive in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FIt added that two other victims,
OL,8,Fstudent Sommacal and recent graduate
OL,9,FGualtieri, were not involved in the
OL,10,Fscientific mission.
OL,12,FCave diving is a highly technical and
OL,13,Fdangerous activity that requires
OL,14,Fspecialised training, equipment and
OL,15,Fstrict safety protocols.
OL,17,FRisks increase sharply in environments
OL,18,Fwhere divers cannot head straight up
OL,19,Fand at depth, particularly when
OL,20,Fconditions are poor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779048354
OL,3,CDivers search for bodies of Italian
OL,4,Cdivers who died during cave dive in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FExperts say it's easy to become
OL,8,Fdisoriented or lost inside caves,
OL,9,Fparticularly as sediment clouds can
OL,10,Fsharply reduce visibility.
OL,12,FDiving at 50 metres also exceeds the
OL,13,Fmaximum depth recommended for
OL,14,Frecreational divers by most major
OL,15,Festablished scuba certifying agencies,
OL,16,Fwith depths beyond 40 metres
OL,17,Fconsidered technical diving and
OL,18,Frequiring specialised training and
OL,19,Fequipment. The recreational diving
OL,20,Flimit in the Maldives is 30 metres.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779048354
OL,3,CDivers search for bodies of Italian
OL,4,Cdivers who died during cave dive in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FShareef said Benedetti's body was
OL,8,Ffound near the mouth of the cave, and
OL,9,Fauthorities believed the remaining
OL,10,Ffour had entered the cave.
OL,12,FTwo Italians, a deep-sea rescue expert
OL,13,Fand a cave diving expert, are expected
OL,14,Fto join the recovery effort, Shareef
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FItalian officials said around 20 other
OL,18,FItalians who were on the same
OL,19,Fexpedition aboard a vessel named the
OL,20,F"Duke of York" were safe.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779048354
OL,3,CDivers search for bodies of Italian
OL,4,Cdivers who died during cave dive in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FItaly's embassy in Colombo was
OL,8,Fproviding assistance to those on board
OL,9,Fand had contacted the Red Crescent,
OL,10,Fwhich offered to deploy volunteers to
OL,11,Fhelp provide psychological aid.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThe Maldives tourism ministry said it
OL,19,Fhas suspended the operating license of
OL,20,Fthe "Duke of York" pending an
OL,21,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@|D@EOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779048354
OL,3,CDivers search for bodies of Italian
OL,4,Cdivers who died during cave dive in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FThe Italian foreign ministry said the
OL,8,Fcave is divided into three large
OL,9,Fchambers connected by narrow passages.
OL,10,FRecovery teams explored two of the
OL,11,Fthree chambers on Friday, but the
OL,12,Fsearch was limited due to
OL,13,Fconsiderations over oxygen and
OL,14,Fdecompression.
OL,16,FOn Saturday, they will explore the
OL,17,Fthird chamber, the ministry added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
